## Basic Information
Targeting information for each MWM target

### Naming Convention
$MWM_ASTRA/0.6.0/summary/mwmTargets-0.6.0.fits.gz

### Releases
DR19

### Enviroments
MWM_ASTRA

### Approximate Size
921 MB

### File Type
FITS

### Generated by Product
astra

### Is a VAC
False

### HDUS List for release DR19
  - [HDU0: PRIMARY](#hdu0-primary)
  - [HDU1](#hdu1)
